#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.roll.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.roll"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:1 of
msgid "Roll tensor elements along a given axis."
msgstr "沿给定轴滚动张量元素。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:3 of
msgid ""
"Elements that roll beyond the last position are re-introduced at the "
"first."
msgstr "滚动超出最后一个位置的元素将重新引入到第一个位置。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:6 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:8 of
msgid ""
"The number of places by which elements are shifted.  If a tuple, then "
"`axis` must be a tuple of the same size, and each of the given axes is "
"shifted by the corresponding number.  If an int while `axis` is a tuple "
"of ints, then the same value is used for all given axes."
msgstr ""
"元素移动的位置数。如果为元组，则 `axis` 必须是相同大小的元组，并且每个"
"给定轴都按相应的数值进行移动。如果为整数而 `axis` 是整数元组，则对所有"
"给定轴使用相同的值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:14 of
msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which elements are shifted.  By default, the tensor is"
" flattened before shifting, after which the original shape is restored."
msgstr "元素移动所沿的轴。默认情况下，在移动之前将张量展平，之后恢复原始形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:19 of
msgid "**res** -- Output tensor, with the same shape as `a`."
msgstr "**res** -- 输出张量，形状与 `a` 相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`rollaxis`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:25 of
msgid "Roll the specified axis backwards, until it lies in a given position."
msgstr "将指定轴向后滚动，直到它位于给定位置。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:28 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:29 of
msgid "Supports rolling over multiple dimensions simultaneously."
msgstr "支持同时在多个维度上进行滚动。"

#: maxframe.tensor.misc.roll.roll:32 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

